y time of SNRs will\nallow us to use SNR catalogs as `SN surveys' to calculate SN rates and delay\ntime distributions in the Local Group.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 16 May 2016 20:01:48 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 7 Oct 2016 19:36:40 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-11-07"}
