 scenarios that will take about 2 to 20 million\nmiles of real-world driving to encounter. This technique thus has the potential\nto reduce greatly the development and validation time for AVs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 16 May 2016 22:11:52 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 16 Jun 2016 03:58:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-11-18"}
