lity. The model\nconsiders steady state solidification at close-to and far-from equilibrium\nconditions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 17 May 2016 02:59:08 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 10 Feb 2017 21:09:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-02-14"}
